    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014it seriously looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every single service schedule. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
